The paper discusses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also involves human-agent interaction, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of demonstrations, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper involves robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it discusses the use of agents and their learning.
